{"tid":786710,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[佛系mode] 有無巴絲打同另一半已經玩到有少少性冷感左？","createTime":"2018-08-20T06:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T15:23:18.000Z","uid":52658,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfe8bd034269e3f04e1c9ef9e13617a6d8803c3","tid":786710,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左三年 <br />\n扑野方面真係咩花式都玩過哂 <br />\n呢排覺得自己開始無咩想搞佢既衝動 <br />\n<br />\n但就係尋晚 佢突然話想著住校服比我搞 <br />\n<br />\n我: 去邊度買校服呀? <br />\n佢: 著番我中學個套囉 <br />\n<br />\n佢係衣櫃拎左套校服出黎著左上身 <br />\n我即刻好似撻著左咁撲低左佢 <br />\n<br />\n我:一齊三年而家先知你讀皇仁<br />\n佢: 嘻嘻 傻豬 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁 <br />\n我地就渡過左激情既夜晚 <br />\n詳細唔多講 <br />\n但我覺得我地既關係已經修補左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586ea2db380d867700f775e20d0feba09ae35a72","tid":786710,"uid":2786,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:37:12.000Z","msg":"皇仁係人都知係男校啦 <br />\n重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9bb33a5455ad4636bbb69a72409deb0da2383f","tid":786710,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"樓主思覺失調 佢A0"},{"pid":"2e4473d7a201e133a28a089645141e727bb08aa9","tid":786710,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"586ea2db380d867700f775e20d0feba09ae35a72","tid":786710,"uid":2786,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:37:12.000Z","msg":"皇仁係人都知係男校啦 <br />\n重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:38:51.000Z","msg":"我真係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1182df06c4ac0c53047abe1848b2fd82cb2c2df3","tid":786710,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"佛你老母"},{"pid":"33185baffa1b0d3d887fd4212c72cdaac886cf47","tid":786710,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20